OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1775481061
OL,3,CMan left with 'potentially life
OL,4,Caltering injuries' after Sheffield
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FPolice are investigating after a man
OL,8,Fwas seriously injured in a shooting in
OL,9,FTinsley.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire police say they were
OL,12,Fcalled to reports of a shooting on
OL,13,FGreasbro Road in the Tinsley area of
OL,14,FSheffield.
OL,16,FArmed police attended just before 11
OL,17,Fo'clock at night on Sunday 5 April,
OL,18,Fwhere they found a man in his 30s with
OL,19,Fserious injuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
