FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1775481061
OL,3,CMan left with 'potentially life
OL,4,Caltering injuries' after Sheffield
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FA police spokesperson said he was
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital "where he remains in
OL,9,Fa stable condition."
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Laura Procter
OL,12,Fsaid: "This is a terrible incident
OL,13,Fthat has left a man with potentially
OL,14,Flife-altering injuries.
OL,16,F"We have a dedicated team of officers
OL,17,Fand staff who are hard at work
OL,18,Ffollowing various lines of enquiries
OL,19,Fto identify those responsible for the
OL,20,Fsenseless act of violence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1775481061
OL,3,CMan left with 'potentially life
OL,4,Caltering injuries' after Sheffield
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,F"Gun crime has no place in South
OL,8,FYorkshire.
OL,10,F"It is not acceptable on our streets,
OL,11,Fand we will relentlessly pursue those
OL,12,Fwho are involved.
OL,14,F"Even the smallest piece of
OL,15,Fintelligence from you could prove
OL,16,Fcrucial to our investigation and we
OL,17,Fwould be particularly keen to hear
OL,18,Ffrom anyone who was in the Greasbro
OL,19,FRoad area at the time and has relevant
OL,20,Fdoorbell, dash cam or CCTV footage."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
